projects.name: Villa de la Neige
projects.project_description: A villa resort for skiers from around the world, Villa de la Neige evokes the feeling of being inside a hotel covered in snow that still retains all the amenities of summer on the Mediterranean: tennis courts, pools, and sunbathing balconies.
